You'd be able to simultaneously increase/decrease the speed of nearby vehicles, allowing your car to pass.<br />
<br />
Or you'd just get &quot;I can't do that, Dave&quot; situations, where the car decides that you need to wait for the next exit, in order to not endanger the people nearby.
